## Summary
This documentation details the Amazon Kinesis Firehose destination integration for Amplitude Data, explaining how to stream Amplitude event data to AWS Kinesis Firehose by creating the necessary AWS resources (stream, IAM role with proper permissions) and configuring the connection in Amplitude's destination catalog.

